    "body": "Ok, the issue was that geth can't sync historic blocks without consensus client. With both working in tandem it works perfectly.\r\n\r\nThe current Ethereum launchpad doesn't reflect those requirements - my assumption was that I could run geth to sync while I set-up the rest of the system. I'd appreciate more clear documentation / errors that geth won't do anything without a consensus client.",
